Title: Corporal Punishment
Plot: While trying to track down a delusional and violent Marine who thinks he's still in Iraq, the NCIS team will learn that the man has been the subject of a secret experiment - and it comes with a high price to pay.
GuestStars: José Zúñiga, Paul Telfer, Amy Carlson, Patrick Fabian, Marcius W. Harris, John Siciliano
